{
  "id": "RAW_477cf6cd",
  "title": "“大模型第一股”打响上市前哨战！智谱 GLM-4.7 刷新开源编程 SOTA，修复代码、终端操作表现超 Claude 4.5",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU1NDA4NjU2MA==&mid=2247651980&idx=1&sn=e25cead9fa0cec056a3526ec83d88b90",
  "date": "2025-12-23 07:27:00",
  "author": "AI前线",
  "siteName": "AI前线",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"325\" data-backw=\"578\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/ZBjVrHIdkOmMFPINXNMvspJAZNLgPic7NKHABZ8DsBoLuSMht3oslIUibh5tQCTfLlmLLlZ9tibVia3Nt5HUyA4y0A/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"2730\" data-cropy2=\"1374.446366782007\" data-imgfileid=\"100168328\" data-ratio=\"0.503125\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"width:578px;height:291px;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=aac1a101&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FZBjVrHIdkOmMFPINXNMvspJAZNLgPic7Nc9zURCxR7oZeju4VWQSqzIztd1ibNEXLJTSv39SEZVibzlOs9cZGibglw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p style=\"font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: #919191;text-align: left;line-height: 1em;margin: 0;margin-top: 13px;padding-left: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">作者 ｜ 木子、高允毅 </span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">正在&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">冲刺大模型第一股</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;的&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">智谱</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，今天又拿出了诚意满满的新一代大模型&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">GLM-4.7，还给开源了</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100168312\" alt=\"image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3287037037037037\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7c6a9221&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZBjVrHIdkOmMFPINXNMvspJAZNLgPic7N4LEnxyd2EEDnYljkowbZG0miaOWXIVmFqopl1xLkEzwOUJyic7cCibQEQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">GLM-4.7</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">主打编程与代理式任务（coding + agentic tasks）的提升</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，同时在&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">推理能力</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;等方面也有所增强。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">众所周知，今年的大模型，已经从卷“会答题”发展成了&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">卷“能干活”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。对应的变化，也体现在评测体系上，这些测试覆盖了真实代码修改、终端操作、多工具调用以及长链路任务执行等场景。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">智谱也是&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">把 GLM-4.7 一口气送进了 17 项基准测试</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，和 GPT-5、Claude Sonnet 4.5、Gemini 3.0 Pro、DeepSeek-V3.2、Kimi K2 Thinking 等同台竞技。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">然后在一众强劲对手中，GLM-4.7 还在&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">两项 BenchMark 中刷新了公开 SOTA</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：在&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">AIME 2025</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">（测试高级数学推理能力）中正确率已达 95.7%；在&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">BrowseComp-ZH</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;中分数达 66.6%。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100168314\" data-ratio=\"0.9324074074074075\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4db96adf&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZBjVrHIdkOmMFPINXNMvspJAZNLgPic7NdJFCQkad7O9ZnSmic7ojEd4t6EpvZG3FFwSuiaD2ibhbKvicOKCNk7zHkg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">另外，它在&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">SWE-bench-Verified</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;得分 73.8%，在&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">LiveCodeBench V6</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;得分 84.9%，超过 Claude Sonnet 4.5，</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">刷新了两项开源 SOTA</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100168313\" alt=\"image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5851851851851851\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=41df3459&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZBjVrHIdkOmMFPINXNMvspJAZNLgPic7NjemRsZboHtVkSkU5E0duLDGuqtL1mc1hibMa9EoA452mknZRmWebCLw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:20px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"font-weight: 500;margin: 38px 0 10px 0;height: 59px;line-height: 85px;color: #4285f4;background: none no-repeat 50% 50%;border-bottom: 2px solid #4285f4;background-size: 57px auto;display: inline-block;background-image: url(&quot;https://image.jido.dev/20251223083724_b2e7d789&quot;);\"><span leaf=\"\">UI 质量飞跃，来看看具体 Case</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">仅凭 BenchMark 的高分或许还不够有说服力，智谱官方也放出了一系列 Case，来&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">直观展示 GLM-4.7 的实用效果如何</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">首先，是</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">前端开发</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">要生成一个普通 HTML 网页，在 GLM-4.7 中基本能一句话搞定，大大减少后期微调时间。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">而且比起上一代生成的布局结构更清晰，配色不容易冲突，组件风格也更统一；而且还能覆盖多种风格，从简约、复古到时尚等应有</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">除了普通 HTML，做一个基于 Web 的交互式体验页面（Interactive Web Experience）也是不在话下。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">比如用同一段 Prompt：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100168315\" data-ratio=\"0.9972222222222222\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=116e029f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZBjVrHIdkOmMFPINXNMvspJAZNLgPic7NpHhypGjbhEouQa8GIY4czPwBcI5jKLgcggy3qOtZZVYfiaUq2Klx0xg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">给前一代 GLM-4.6，生成效果是这样的：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100168324\" data-ratio=\"0.6327433628318584\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"904\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=22647ad3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FZBjVrHIdkOmMFPINXNMvspJAZNLgPic7NS9HanI7ICllMh8DjdJztib0J5whAUbia2uWfE5KB1AKlALyica7D2ppSw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">而给 GLM-4.7 生成的 UI 质量就提升了一大截，比如其动态效果和 3D 交互感都明显增强了。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100168319\" data-ratio=\"0.6327433628318584\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"904\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cbfe891c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FZBjVrHIdkOmMFPINXNMvspJAZNLgPic7NeW96Q9YQeuvpOmKpFVd3IjTYI8VibVUWZt6BIBW7icNicC2vhSuz0D6MA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">GLM-4.7 体现出的高级审美能力，还在&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“艺术作品”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;的 3D 展示中带来质的飞跃。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">它在空间层次、透视关系上处理得很清楚，同时在配色、材质对比、景深和构图上也下了功夫；该亮的地方亮，该收的地方收。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">比如要生成一个花园空间，中间是一座装饰华丽的宝塔，周围被盛开的樱花树包围，GLM-4.7 的作品既有体积像素的 3D 感，又美观和谐。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-imgfileid=\"100168325\" data-ratio=\"0.659375\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b0c5babc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZBjVrHIdkOmMFPINXNMvspJAZNLgPic7NYok65rlcsrDgHXUaNpKg4yTVBicfrJ1ML13rYTAl7ibaub7V4p8R5zeQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">另外，在&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">幻灯片制作</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;上，GLM-4.7 也明显&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“好看了”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">PPT16:9 的适配率从 52% 提升至 91%</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">生成的页面布局更准确、元素比例更舒服，整体观感更接近一份可以直接拿去用的成品。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">这样的审美同样体现在&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">海报设计</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;上，</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">排版与配色更加灵活，具备设计感。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">同样设计以“巴黎”为主题的海报，GLM-4.7 明显从配色和排版上更胜一筹，懂得突出主题，注意文字比例和位置，图片的镶嵌和配色，而不是死板的罗列排布。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">不少网友也对使用效果给出好评，称体验的效果很不错。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100168316\" alt=\"image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2001906577693041\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1049\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=db1862fe&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZBjVrHIdkOmMFPINXNMvspJAZNLgPic7N1QdXoZabyaM5aPbeyv86zfaWiaiawicEF9sQsd27jAZtaU89ZIBSVMHRQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100168317\" alt=\"image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.16312741312741313\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1036\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d59c3cc3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZBjVrHIdkOmMFPINXNMvspJAZNLgPic7NtxqDz2fB62ZrSSsGicoOoo0nicKickpibaKlWx3UI9Wu6T8NWFBeWXHxFg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">也有网友提出，还想看看 GLM-4.7 与最牛编码模型 Opus4.5 之间的比拼。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100168318\" data-ratio=\"0.22275334608030592\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1046\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=25ae00b6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZBjVrHIdkOmMFPINXNMvspJAZNLgPic7N6UUUA27Pd5fAGTPSKE1URBibfiackQxFUmV2KnulW25fuKlKI0NQwTew%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:20px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"font-weight: 500;margin: 38px 0 10px 0;height: 59px;line-height: 85px;color: #4285f4;background: none no-repeat 50% 50%;border-bottom: 2px solid #4285f4;background-size: 57px auto;display: inline-block;background-image: url(&quot;https://image.jido.dev/20251223083724_b2e7d789&quot;);\"><span leaf=\"\">GLM-4.7 的三种“思考模式”</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">那么，GLM-4.7 为什么能有这样的进步？</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">在推理机制上，GLM-4.7 围绕&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“如何在复杂任务中更稳定地思考与行动”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;这一核心问题，对模型的思维流程进行了系统性重构。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">形成了由“</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">交织式思考（Interleaved Thinking）+ 保留式思考（Preserved Thinking）+ 轮级思考（Turn-level Thinking）”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;组成的一整套推理机制。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">具体而言，</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">交错式思考</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，指的是 GLM-4.7 在每次响应和工具调用之前都会进行思考。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">这其实是自 GLM-4.5 起就引入的基础能力，GLM-4.7 对其进行了强化，使模型在每一次生成回复或调用工具之前，都会先进行内部推理，再决定下一步行动，从而提升指令遵循的准确性和生成质量。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">保留式思考</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，指的是在编码代理场景中，GLM-4.7 能够自动保留多轮对话中的所有思维模块，重用现有推理过程，而不是从头开始重新推导。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">这主要用于多回合、长链路任务中，减少了信息丢失和不一致的情况。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">最后，</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">轮级思考</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;就是 GLM-4.7 支持对会话内的推理进行逐回合控制，允许在同一会话内按回合决定是否启用推理。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">对于简单、低复杂度的请求可以关闭思考以降低延迟和计算成本，而在需要精确决策和稳定执行的任务中再开启完整推理流程。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100168323\" data-ratio=\"0.7648148148148148\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f2740657&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZBjVrHIdkOmMFPINXNMvspJAZNLgPic7N465p7mNso1Aexwh3SLFgia1KxFCzm6PshicyM7pCUiaIZxlGkViahn9J4g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">通过这套“推理组合拳”，GLM-4.7 在复杂任务中的行为表现更加稳定连贯，也更容易控制；这为其在代理式编程和长周期任务执行中提供了关键的技术基础。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:20px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"font-weight: 500;margin: 38px 0 10px 0;height: 59px;line-height: 85px;color: #4285f4;background: none no-repeat 50% 50%;border-bottom: 2px solid #4285f4;background-size: 57px auto;display: inline-block;background-image: url(&quot;https://image.jido.dev/20251223083724_b2e7d789&quot;);\"><span leaf=\"\">智谱冲刺“大模型第一股”</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">在冲刺“大模型第一股”的前夕，智谱用一次技术密度极高的模型更新，主动把自己推到聚光灯下。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">这里再来简单回顾一下智谱的上市细节。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">12 月 19 日，港交所官网披露，北京大模型公司智谱已通过聆讯，IPO 招股书同步公开。这意味着，智谱正式迈入上市冲刺的最后阶段。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">按招股书口径，公司最新估值为&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">243.77 亿元</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，中国大模型公司第一次以如此完整的姿态，走到公开市场面前。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">从经营数据看，智谱仍处在典型的高速放量阶段。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">2022—2024 年，公司收入从 0.6 亿元增长至 3.1 亿元；而真正的拐点出现在 2025 年上半年：2024H1 收入仅 0.4 亿元，2025H1 已跃升至 1.9 亿元，同比增幅超过 300%。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">其中，近&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">85% 的收入</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;来自本地化部署，客户覆盖互联网、公共服务、电信和传统企业；MaaS 平台则通过持续降价放大调用规模，2025H1 云端机构客户增至 3061 家，并对本地化部署形成明显引流。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">但另一条曲线同样陡峭。招股书显示，</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">智谱的亏损扩张速度远快于收入增长</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">2022—2024 年及 2025H1，经调整净亏损分别为 0.97 亿元、6.21 亿元、24.66 亿元和 17.52 亿元，几乎全部指向</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">研发投入</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">同一时期，研发费用从 0.8 亿元升至 22.0 亿元，算力相关支出占比超过 70%。毛利率仍维持在 50% 以上，但在 MaaS 价格战中持续承压。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">把时间轴往前拉，这其实是一家成立不到 6 年的公司。</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">智谱成立于 2019 年、脱胎于清华大学知识工程实验室（KEG）</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，是国内最早一批独立大模型公司之一。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">从&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">GLM 架构</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;起步，它就选择了一条清晰却昂贵的路径：</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">持续把资源押注在模型能力本身。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;截至 2025 年，</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">其模型已支持约 8000 万台设备、服务超过 1.2 万家机构客户</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">开源链接：</span></span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">GitHub：<a href=\"https://github.com/zai-org/GLM-4.5\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/zai-org/GLM-4.5</a></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Hugging Face：huggingface.co/zai-org/GLM-4.7</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">魔搭社区：<a href=\"https://modelscope.cn/models/ZhipuAI/GLM-4.7\" target=\"_blank\">https://modelscope.cn/models/ZhipuAI/GLM-4.7</a></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">参考链接：</span></span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://z.ai/blog/glm-4.7\" target=\"_blank\">https://z.ai/blog/glm-4.7</a></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://x.com/Zai_org/status/2003156119087382683\" target=\"_blank\">https://x.com/Zai_org/status/2003156119087382683</a></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyMzI3NzQ0Mg==&amp;mid=2247492642&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=2ab783f2e238ff6025b25f3cf0aa1258&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"GLM-4.7上线并开源：更强的编码\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">GLM-4.7上线并开源：更强的编码</span></a></span></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "智谱发布并开源了新一代大模型 GLM-4.7，在编程与代理式任务、推理能力方面显著提升，刷新多项 SOTA，并详细介绍了其“交织式思考”、“保留式思考”和“轮级思考”三种推理机制。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "智谱发布并开源了新一代大模型 GLM-4.7，在编程与代理式任务、推理能力方面显著提升，刷新多项 SOTA，并详细介绍了其“交织式思考”、“保留式思考”和“轮级思考”三种推理机制。",
  "summary": "文章报道了智谱公司发布并开源其最新大模型 GLM-4.7，该模型主要在编程和代理式任务上取得了显著进步，同时在推理能力方面也有所增强。GLM-4.7 在多项 BenchMark 测试中表现出色，尤其在 AIME 2025 和 BrowseComp-ZH 两项中刷新了公开 SOTA，并在 SWE-bench-Verified 和 LiveCodeBench V6 中超越 Claude Sonnet 4.5，刷新了开源 SOTA。文章通过前端开发、3D 艺术作品生成和幻灯片制作等具体案例，展示了 GLM-4.7 在 UI 质量和美学方面的飞跃，证明了其高级审美能力。技术层面，文章揭示了 GLM-4.7 之所以能取得这些进步，得益于其重构的推理机制，包括“交织式思考”、“保留式思考”和“轮级思考”，这使其在复杂任务中表现更稳定可控。最后，文章结合智谱冲刺“大模型第一股”的背景，介绍了其上市进程和财务数据，强调了智谱持续投入模型能力研发的战略，并暗示了 GLM-4.7 的发布是其上市前的重要技术里程碑，彰显其核心竞争力。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "GLM-4.7 在编程与代理式任务取得重大突破，多项基准测试刷新 SOTA",
      "explanation": "GLM-4.7 在 SWE-bench-Verified 和 LiveCodeBench V6 等编程基准测试中得分领先，并刷新了两项开源 SOTA，显示其在代码修复、终端操作等方面的强大能力超越竞品。这不仅提升了开发效率，也为自动化软件开发和 Agent 应用奠定了基础。"
    },
    {
      "point": "GLM-4.7 展现卓越的 UI 生成和美学设计能力，大幅提升内容可用性和视觉吸引力",
      "explanation": "通过前端网页、3D 艺术作品、幻灯片和海报设计案例，GLM-4.7 的生成结果在布局、配色、动态效果和整体审美上都有明显提升，能够生成更接近成品的视觉内容，这对于产品设计、营销创意等领域具有实际价值。"
